1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:29,980
[SPEAKER_01] Svećenik, moji brat, ratni drug, Željko Guberović, koji je pripada, on je iskupio,

2
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:35,899
[SPEAKER_01] pripada biskupi Newarka. Evo, ja sam tiio snimiti ime malo kao jedan intervju,

3
00:00:35,899 --> 00:00:41,619
[SPEAKER_01] jedno njegovo svjelčanstvo životno koje je po meni jako, koje može pomoć drugima,

4
00:00:41,619 --> 00:00:47,500
[SPEAKER_01] i jako konkretno, zato što je Željko bio, ne znam do koje godine.

5
00:00:47,500 --> 00:00:48,560
[SPEAKER_00] Do 30.

6
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:53,679
[SPEAKER_01] Do 30. godine, ateista, malo kontradiktorni, ateista on kaže, jer je mrzio Bog.

7
00:00:53,679 --> 00:00:58,820
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, da ne dužim, ja bih predao njemu riječ, pa ću te malo prekidati,

8
00:00:58,820 --> 00:01:03,740
[SPEAKER_01] tako, ja znam isto, dosta pađu, ako budem tiio nešto naglasiti.

9
00:01:03,740 --> 00:01:07,819
[SPEAKER_01] Eto, Željko, kako si živo taj ateista od 30. godine?

10
00:01:07,819 --> 00:01:13,159
[SPEAKER_01] Bio si kemičar, radio si u Kini, uspješan čovjek, ali u dubini, e.

11
00:01:13,159 --> 00:01:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] Dobre, prvo da objasnim to, da je nelogično biti ateista, koji mrzi Boga,

12
00:01:20,159 --> 00:01:25,180
[SPEAKER_00] neki ne uhvate odmah da je, kako možeš mrziti ono što ne postoji.

13
00:01:25,180 --> 00:01:31,900
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ja sam odrastao u obitelji gdje moji raditelji su moli,

14
00:01:31,900 --> 00:01:34,159
[SPEAKER_00] ali u komunizmu nisu išli u crkvu.

15
00:01:34,159 --> 00:01:42,780
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da sam bio kršćen, primio prvu pričest, potvrdu.

16
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:48,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ali od potvrde jedno što se sjećam da sam dobio ručni sat na poklon.

17
00:01:48,420 --> 00:01:51,879
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to mi ništa nije bilo važno, nisam...

18
00:01:51,879 --> 00:01:54,780
[SPEAKER_01] Želiko mi ono zapora, svako toliko mu ću morat napomenuti riječ,

19
00:01:54,780 --> 00:01:58,359
[SPEAKER_01] jer u Americi dugo priča engleski i španjolski tamo.

20
00:01:58,359 --> 00:02:00,980
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da svako toliko mora ka prisjetit hrvatsko riječ.

21
00:02:00,980 --> 00:02:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

22
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:07,840
[SPEAKER_00] Imao sam ono osnove, znao sam nešto vjere,

23
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:11,259
[SPEAKER_00] ali mi nije, svako nisam jao nijakav odnos s Bogom,

24
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,680
[SPEAKER_00] to mi ništa nije značilo.

25
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:16,280
[SPEAKER_00] I kad sam...

26
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:19,900
[SPEAKER_00] Bio sam vrlo uspješan u kemiji,

27
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:22,759
[SPEAKER_00] išao sam na takmičenja iz kemije u ovoj školi.

28
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je moj otac odlučio da me pošalje

29
00:02:26,599 --> 00:02:29,479
[SPEAKER_00] u kemijsku tehničku školu u Zagreb.

30
00:02:29,479 --> 00:02:30,759
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo iz Koprivnice.

31
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:37,080
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam, kao i svaki tineđer, se kažem,

32
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] sam htio osloboditi se svoje utjecaje, svoje majke.

33
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:44,979
[SPEAKER_00] jer ona bi dosta me kontrolira,

34
00:02:44,979 --> 00:02:47,759
[SPEAKER_00] uvek je bila u panici, šta će mi se dogoditi.

35
00:02:47,759 --> 00:02:53,139
[SPEAKER_00] I išao sam u Zagreb, u školu,

36
00:02:53,139 --> 00:02:56,819
[SPEAKER_00] u devetom mjesecu, sretan, što sam se oslobodio svoje majke.

37
00:02:56,819 --> 00:02:59,479
[SPEAKER_00] I dva mjeseca kasnije ona je umrla.

38
00:02:59,479 --> 00:03:04,439
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon smrti moje majke, ja sam se povukao potpuno.

39
00:03:04,439 --> 00:03:05,840
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko smo godina kada je umrla majka?

40
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:07,099
[SPEAKER_00] 14 godina.

41
00:03:07,099 --> 00:03:08,300
[SPEAKER_00] Jako brzo umro je tata.

42
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:11,360
[SPEAKER_00] Onda sam se povukao u samoću.

43
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:13,900
[SPEAKER_00] Bio sam potpuno odvojeno od ljudi.

44
00:03:13,900 --> 00:03:16,620
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan prijatelj se nije da odvojiti od mene.

45
00:03:16,620 --> 00:03:20,740
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, kad sam bio,

46
00:03:20,740 --> 00:03:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] par, dvije godine kasnije,

47
00:03:23,539 --> 00:03:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] sam počeo pušiti

48
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,919
[SPEAKER_00] da bi imao razloga da budem s ljudima.

49
00:03:26,919 --> 00:03:28,740
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam više znao komunicirati.

50
00:03:30,319 --> 00:03:35,039
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je, kad sam imao sedamnaest godina,

51
00:03:35,039 --> 00:03:36,639
[SPEAKER_00] moj otac je umro.

52
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:40,780
[SPEAKER_00] I opet sam se počeo povlačiti.

53
00:03:40,780 --> 00:03:43,680
[SPEAKER_00] Počeo sam pit.

54
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:48,379
[SPEAKER_00] Do tem jere da sam uvijek imao bolj,

55
00:03:48,379 --> 00:03:50,819
[SPEAKER_00] bocu ruma u džepu,

56
00:03:50,819 --> 00:03:53,659
[SPEAKER_00] tako da uvijek imam isti nivo alkohola u krvi.

57
00:03:54,659 --> 00:03:56,580
[SPEAKER_00] Pušio sam do tri kutije dnevno.

58
00:03:56,580 --> 00:03:59,860
[SPEAKER_00] Bio sam ovisan o seksualnoj ovisnosti,

59
00:03:59,860 --> 00:04:01,620
[SPEAKER_00] pornografije i tako.

60
00:04:01,620 --> 00:04:06,240
[SPEAKER_00] I to svako dovode do toga da se preziraš.

61
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,939
[SPEAKER_00] Nije važno ako si ateist.

62
00:04:07,939 --> 00:04:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] Nije važno ako mišliš da to nije grijeh.

63
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:15,199
[SPEAKER_00] Niko ne može živit tako da se ne prezire.

64
00:04:15,199 --> 00:04:17,180
[SPEAKER_00] Onda,

65
00:04:17,180 --> 00:04:20,860
[SPEAKER_00] među vremenu sam bio uspešan u svom poslu.

66
00:04:20,860 --> 00:04:22,100
[SPEAKER_00] Počeo sam raditi.

67
00:04:23,019 --> 00:04:24,680
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo interesantan posao

68
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,980
[SPEAKER_00] u privatnoj firmi

69
00:04:26,980 --> 00:04:29,800
[SPEAKER_00] i posle u švicarskoj firmi.

70
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:33,120
[SPEAKER_00] Radio sam u Kini.

71
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,939
[SPEAKER_00] To me je držalo.

72
00:04:34,939 --> 00:04:37,040
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad sam joo 25 godina,

73
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,819
[SPEAKER_00] moj brat je umro.

74
00:04:38,819 --> 00:04:44,079
[SPEAKER_00] To me više nije uništilo.

75
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:46,439
[SPEAKER_00] Smrt oca me uništilo potpuno.

76
00:04:46,439 --> 00:04:49,060
[SPEAKER_00] Jer umeđu vremenu,

77
00:04:49,060 --> 00:04:50,660
[SPEAKER_00] nakon smrti majke,

78
00:04:50,660 --> 00:04:52,319
[SPEAKER_00] on mi je postao puno bliži,

79
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:54,399
[SPEAKER_00] biće na joj otac kao prijatelj.

80
00:04:54,399 --> 00:04:56,560
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je brat umro,

81
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:58,100
[SPEAKER_00] više ništa nisam osjećao.

82
00:04:58,100 --> 00:05:00,939
[SPEAKER_00] Misledno me više ništa ne može uništiti.

83
00:05:00,939 --> 00:05:03,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ali onda,

84
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:04,319
[SPEAKER_00] dvije godine,

85
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:06,540
[SPEAKER_00] par godina nakon što je on umro,

86
00:05:06,540 --> 00:05:08,240
[SPEAKER_00] moja nečekanje,

87
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:10,939
[SPEAKER_00] ovak čerka je bila dobila skizofreniju.

88
00:05:10,939 --> 00:05:11,980
[SPEAKER_00] To me uništilo.

89
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:16,779
[SPEAKER_00] jer svaki posjećivao sam je u Zagrebu,

90
00:05:16,779 --> 00:05:17,379
[SPEAKER_00] u bolnici,

91
00:05:17,379 --> 00:05:19,879
[SPEAKER_00] posjećivao sam je svaki dan.

92
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:24,839
[SPEAKER_00] I svaka posjeta me uništila.

93
00:05:24,839 --> 00:05:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] Potpuno iscijedila svoj snagu koju sam imao.

94
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:30,139
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da,

95
00:05:30,139 --> 00:05:33,220
[SPEAKER_00] nikad nisam znao šta će se,

96
00:05:33,220 --> 00:05:35,699
[SPEAKER_00] šta očekivati kad dođeš u bolnicu.

97
00:05:35,699 --> 00:05:38,740
[SPEAKER_00] i uvek je bilo neugodno iznađenje.

98
00:05:38,740 --> 00:05:41,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ta bolestne čakinje te dovela

99
00:05:41,019 --> 00:05:42,060
[SPEAKER_00] malo da tražiš pomoć.

100
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:43,600
[SPEAKER_00] Tako si došao i do svećanika.

101
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:46,160
[SPEAKER_00] U to vreme sam radio

102
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:49,540
[SPEAKER_00] u švicarskoj firmi.

103
00:05:49,540 --> 00:05:52,079
[SPEAKER_00] Moj šef je...

104
00:05:52,079 --> 00:05:52,839
[SPEAKER_00] A, bio je kršćan.

105
00:05:52,839 --> 00:05:54,240
[SPEAKER_00] On je bio kršćan

106
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,920
[SPEAKER_00] i nije mogao podnositi

107
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:58,399
[SPEAKER_00] da u njegovoj ekipi

108
00:05:58,399 --> 00:06:00,279
[SPEAKER_00] je neko ko tvrde da je ateist.

109
00:06:00,279 --> 00:06:02,300
[SPEAKER_00] Pa me na jednom poslom večeri

110
00:06:02,300 --> 00:06:03,579
[SPEAKER_00] dva sata gnjavio

111
00:06:03,579 --> 00:06:05,139
[SPEAKER_00] da me Bog voli.

112
00:06:05,699 --> 00:06:10,579
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je dobio samo cinizam od mene.

113
00:06:10,579 --> 00:06:11,220
[SPEAKER_00] Cinizam?

114
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:13,079
[SPEAKER_01] A ti si rekao...

115
00:06:13,079 --> 00:06:13,899
[SPEAKER_01] Kako si rekao?

116
00:06:13,899 --> 00:06:15,939
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je to ljubav da su mi svi pomrli

117
00:06:15,939 --> 00:06:17,180
[SPEAKER_01] neka nekog drugog.

118
00:06:17,180 --> 00:06:18,839
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ja sam mu rekao

119
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:22,379
[SPEAKER_00] ako je to ljubav

120
00:06:22,379 --> 00:06:25,339
[SPEAKER_00] da mi je majka umrla,

121
00:06:25,339 --> 00:06:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] da mi je otac umro,

122
00:06:26,420 --> 00:06:27,540
[SPEAKER_00] da mi je brat umro,

123
00:06:27,540 --> 00:06:29,660
[SPEAKER_00] da mi je nečaka bolestna,

124
00:06:29,660 --> 00:06:31,860
[SPEAKER_00] reci dom Bogu da me prestane voliti.

125
00:06:31,860 --> 00:06:34,819
[SPEAKER_00] A on se nije predao

126
00:06:34,819 --> 00:06:36,740
[SPEAKER_00] nego je počeo govoriti o molitvi,

127
00:06:36,740 --> 00:06:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] na što sam ja isto odgovorio nešto cinično,

128
00:06:40,199 --> 00:06:42,040
[SPEAKER_00] on se sjećam njegovog odgovora.

129
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:42,740
[SPEAKER_00] On je rekao

130
00:06:42,740 --> 00:06:46,839
[SPEAKER_00] ti si kemičar.

131
00:06:46,839 --> 00:06:47,740
[SPEAKER_00] Kemičar uvijek

132
00:06:47,740 --> 00:06:50,420
[SPEAKER_00] prvo napravi pokus,

133
00:06:50,420 --> 00:06:51,420
[SPEAKER_00] onda napravi

134
00:06:51,420 --> 00:06:53,480
[SPEAKER_00] zaključak.

135
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,620
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto ne napraviš pokus sa molitvom?

136
00:06:56,660 --> 00:06:58,339
[SPEAKER_00] što zvuči logično,

137
00:06:58,339 --> 00:06:59,360
[SPEAKER_00] meni je bilo,

138
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,319
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam rekao,

139
00:07:00,319 --> 00:07:02,699
[SPEAKER_00] to je preglup pokus da bi ja probao.

140
00:07:02,699 --> 00:07:06,360
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam ni imao svako,

141
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,779
[SPEAKER_00] ni najmanje namjere

142
00:07:07,779 --> 00:07:09,319
[SPEAKER_00] probati molitvu.

143
00:07:09,319 --> 00:07:12,220
[SPEAKER_00] I jedno, ne znam koliko,

144
00:07:12,220 --> 00:07:13,339
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo kratko vrijeme,

145
00:07:13,339 --> 00:07:14,120
[SPEAKER_00] posle toga,

146
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] moja nečaka je pokušala sam ubijstvo,

147
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] preživila je

148
00:07:18,420 --> 00:07:21,379
[SPEAKER_00] i ja sam

149
00:07:21,379 --> 00:07:23,680
[SPEAKER_00] bio,

150
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:26,180
[SPEAKER_00] nisam vidio sam

151
00:07:26,180 --> 00:07:27,759
[SPEAKER_00] da doktori ne mogu pomoći,

152
00:07:27,759 --> 00:07:28,879
[SPEAKER_00] što god oni radili,

153
00:07:28,879 --> 00:07:30,620
[SPEAKER_00] sve gore i gore.

154
00:07:30,620 --> 00:07:32,300
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju krajeva ja sam zaključio

155
00:07:32,300 --> 00:07:35,459
[SPEAKER_00] da zdravog čovjeka staviš u tu bolnicu,

156
00:07:35,459 --> 00:07:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] bi poludio,

157
00:07:36,139 --> 00:07:37,259
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam kako može

158
00:07:37,259 --> 00:07:39,139
[SPEAKER_00] neko zdraviti tamo.

159
00:07:39,139 --> 00:07:40,899
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da sam,

160
00:07:40,899 --> 00:07:43,759
[SPEAKER_00] da sam

161
00:07:43,759 --> 00:07:45,579
[SPEAKER_00] odlučio na kraju

162
00:07:45,579 --> 00:07:47,139
[SPEAKER_00] u očaju

163
00:07:47,139 --> 00:07:48,740
[SPEAKER_00] otići u crkvu

164
00:07:48,740 --> 00:07:49,959
[SPEAKER_00] i moliti

165
00:07:49,959 --> 00:07:53,279
[SPEAKER_00] nekoga da ide razgovarati s njom,

166
00:07:53,279 --> 00:07:54,040
[SPEAKER_00] da je u vjeri,

167
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,480
[SPEAKER_00] da ne baci svoj život.

168
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:58,920
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam očekivao

169
00:07:58,920 --> 00:07:59,420
[SPEAKER_00] od crkve,

170
00:07:59,420 --> 00:08:00,579
[SPEAKER_00] kao institucije,

171
00:08:00,579 --> 00:08:00,959
[SPEAKER_00] ništa,

172
00:08:00,959 --> 00:08:02,779
[SPEAKER_00] samo da neko možda

173
00:08:02,779 --> 00:08:04,319
[SPEAKER_00] može naći načinu

174
00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:05,740
[SPEAKER_00] da je u vjeri

175
00:08:05,740 --> 00:08:07,079
[SPEAKER_00] da život ima smisla,

176
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:09,740
[SPEAKER_00] da se ne ubije.

177
00:08:09,740 --> 00:08:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] Jer kako bi ja te isto

178
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:12,800
[SPEAKER_00] u to uvjerio?

179
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:13,160
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

180
00:08:13,319 --> 00:08:15,139
[SPEAKER_00] te isto ne može.

181
00:08:15,139 --> 00:08:16,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, na kraju krajeva,

182
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:18,040
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam bio u napasti

183
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,379
[SPEAKER_00] za samoubistvu

184
00:08:19,379 --> 00:08:20,279
[SPEAKER_00] u to doba isto.

185
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:20,959
[SPEAKER_00] Ali,

186
00:08:20,959 --> 00:08:22,720
[SPEAKER_00] ako sam,

187
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:24,740
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam razmišljao o samoubistvu,

188
00:08:24,740 --> 00:08:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] razmišljao sam kako napraviti

189
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] da niko ne skonta

190
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,019
[SPEAKER_00] da je bilo

191
00:08:29,019 --> 00:08:29,839
[SPEAKER_00] samoubistvo.

192
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:31,019
[SPEAKER_00] tad si već živio

193
00:08:31,019 --> 00:08:31,819
[SPEAKER_00] s nekom djevojkom,

194
00:08:31,819 --> 00:08:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] da,

195
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] da,

196
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,820
[SPEAKER_00] bio sam 12 godina

197
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:35,980
[SPEAKER_00] s jednom djevojkom

198
00:08:35,980 --> 00:08:38,620
[SPEAKER_00] i ubrzo nakon što je moja nečaka

199
00:08:38,620 --> 00:08:39,860
[SPEAKER_00] ušlo u bolnicu,

