00:14:34,919 --> 00:14:37,080
[SPEAKER_00] vidio sam puno ljudi,

422
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,519
[SPEAKER_00] da idu na ispovijed,

423
00:14:38,519 --> 00:14:39,899
[SPEAKER_00] ispovijede se,

424
00:14:39,899 --> 00:14:40,980
[SPEAKER_00] i ne pomaže,

425
00:14:40,980 --> 00:14:41,759
[SPEAKER_00] zašto?

426
00:14:41,759 --> 00:14:43,779
[SPEAKER_00] Jer oni nisu sebi oprostili.

427
00:14:43,779 --> 00:14:45,840
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da je puno ljudi,

428
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,139
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam rekao,

429
00:14:47,340 --> 00:14:49,279
[SPEAKER_00] molim Boga da ti pomogne,

430
00:14:49,279 --> 00:14:50,500
[SPEAKER_00] da sebi oprostiš.

431
00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] I da Duh Sveti pritisne tipku delete.

432
00:14:52,460 --> 00:14:52,980
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

433
00:14:52,980 --> 00:14:55,340
[SPEAKER_00] Jer Bog je oprostio greha.

434
00:14:55,340 --> 00:14:56,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ako mi sebi da je oprostimo,

435
00:14:56,899 --> 00:14:58,639
[SPEAKER_00] čuvamo ih dalje.

436
00:14:58,639 --> 00:15:01,279
[SPEAKER_00] I, ovaj,

437
00:15:01,279 --> 00:15:06,360
[SPEAKER_00] i znak da sam oprostio ostalima,

438
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:08,320
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo u ovom slučaju Srpima je,

439
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:11,399
[SPEAKER_00] pod nekoliko godina poslije sam bio,

440
00:15:11,399 --> 00:15:12,559
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam bio u Sjemnišu,

441
00:15:12,559 --> 00:15:15,519
[SPEAKER_00] sam bio poslan u misiji u Srbiju,

442
00:15:15,519 --> 00:15:16,340
[SPEAKER_00] dvije godine,

443
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:18,320
[SPEAKER_00] da Bog nije promijenio moje srce,

444
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:19,220
[SPEAKER_00] to ne bi bilo mogo.

445
00:15:19,220 --> 00:15:20,580
[SPEAKER_00] I tamo sam da ja upoznao bio...

446
00:15:20,580 --> 00:15:24,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, nismo se upoznali kad smo išli u Sjemnište.

447
00:15:24,220 --> 00:15:25,759
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si išao u Njuark, ja si išao u Pulu,

448
00:15:25,759 --> 00:15:27,179
[SPEAKER_01] i onda smo se posle našli u Srbiji,

449
00:15:27,179 --> 00:15:28,259
[SPEAKER_01] bili zajedno dvije godine,

450
00:15:28,259 --> 00:15:30,279
[SPEAKER_01] od tada smo ratni drugovi.

451
00:15:30,279 --> 00:15:30,820
[SPEAKER_01] Tako.

452
00:15:31,639 --> 00:15:35,179
[SPEAKER_01] i u stvari kad su me posle u Srbiju...

453
00:15:35,179 --> 00:15:37,580
[SPEAKER_01] sjećaš se stojadina koji smo vozili tamo,

454
00:15:37,580 --> 00:15:39,919
[SPEAKER_01] kad smo imali, imali smo evangelizaciju,

455
00:15:39,919 --> 00:15:41,139
[SPEAKER_01] žijeli smo u Šabcu,

456
00:15:41,139 --> 00:15:43,860
[SPEAKER_01] imali smo evangelizaciju u Vojvodini,

457
00:15:43,860 --> 00:15:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] tamo u Katoličkoj crkvi u Subotici,

458
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:46,379
[SPEAKER_01] u Žoržinu,

459
00:15:46,379 --> 00:15:47,320
[SPEAKER_01] da imali smo jedan stojadin,

460
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:49,100
[SPEAKER_01] koji je jako bio dosta,

461
00:15:49,100 --> 00:15:50,720
[SPEAKER_01] onda ga je preticali na cesti,

462
00:15:51,399 --> 00:15:52,159
[SPEAKER_01] a kad mi on dolazi,

463
00:15:52,159 --> 00:15:53,399
[SPEAKER_01] imali smo ovojica osjećaj

464
00:15:53,399 --> 00:15:56,440
[SPEAKER_01] da nećemo uspjeti pretići,

465
00:15:56,440 --> 00:15:57,480
[SPEAKER_01] onda smo ovako spontano

466
00:15:57,480 --> 00:15:58,500
[SPEAKER_01] sa tijelom ga gurali

467
00:15:58,500 --> 00:16:00,139
[SPEAKER_01] i stvarno ga je malo pomicalo

468
00:16:00,139 --> 00:16:00,559
[SPEAKER_01] da ide to.

469
00:16:00,559 --> 00:16:01,220
[SPEAKER_01] Se čini, ja...

470
00:16:01,220 --> 00:16:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ovako smo ovojica radili,

471
00:16:02,539 --> 00:16:05,379
[SPEAKER_01] da to mu je malo lakše.

472
00:16:05,379 --> 00:16:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo romantično vrijeme,

473
00:16:08,539 --> 00:16:09,039
[SPEAKER_00] sjećam se.

474
00:16:09,039 --> 00:16:12,120
[SPEAKER_00] I još jedna stvar,

475
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] baš sa iskustvom Srbije,

476
00:16:14,539 --> 00:16:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] da kad sam ja išao u Srbiju,

477
00:16:17,539 --> 00:16:19,779
[SPEAKER_00] bio sam u krizi u Sjemništu

478
00:16:19,779 --> 00:16:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] i tamo u Srbiji

479
00:16:21,340 --> 00:16:22,860
[SPEAKER_00] sam ponovo našao radost.

480
00:16:22,860 --> 00:16:24,940
[SPEAKER_00] Često puta upravo...

481
00:16:24,940 --> 00:16:26,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ja isto.

482
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:27,100
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to mi je bilo

483
00:16:27,100 --> 00:16:28,379
[SPEAKER_01] najveća pustinja u životu,

484
00:16:28,379 --> 00:16:30,320
[SPEAKER_01] a Bog mi je najviše govorio tamo.

485
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:30,799
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

486
00:16:30,799 --> 00:16:33,159
[SPEAKER_01] I često puta to govorim,

487
00:16:33,159 --> 00:16:37,700
[SPEAKER_00] da kad ti Bog pomogne

488
00:16:37,700 --> 00:16:39,299
[SPEAKER_00] da možeš voliti nekoga

489
00:16:39,299 --> 00:16:42,559
[SPEAKER_00] kojeg ljudski ne bi mogao voliti,

490
00:16:42,559 --> 00:16:43,580
[SPEAKER_00] kao u tom slučaju

491
00:16:43,580 --> 00:16:44,879
[SPEAKER_00] za mene su bili Srbi,

492
00:16:44,879 --> 00:16:48,700
[SPEAKER_00] onda osjećaš da ljubav Božja

493
00:16:48,700 --> 00:16:49,759
[SPEAKER_00] prolazi kroz tebe.

494
00:16:49,779 --> 00:16:51,340
[SPEAKER_00] nije da sam ja svojom snagom

495
00:16:51,340 --> 00:16:53,299
[SPEAKER_00] volio te ljude,

496
00:16:53,299 --> 00:16:55,179
[SPEAKER_00] nego ljubav Božja

497
00:16:55,179 --> 00:16:56,799
[SPEAKER_00] prolazila kroz mene

498
00:16:56,799 --> 00:16:57,679
[SPEAKER_00] i na taj način

499
00:16:57,679 --> 00:16:59,620
[SPEAKER_00] iskušiš pristutnost Božja.

500
00:16:59,620 --> 00:17:01,299
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, važnji od Srb,

501
00:17:01,299 --> 00:17:02,559
[SPEAKER_00] važnji od drugih naroda,

502
00:17:02,559 --> 00:17:04,460
[SPEAKER_01] su na naši blišći.

503
00:17:04,460 --> 00:17:06,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ja teba poznajem kao čovjeka

504
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:07,339
[SPEAKER_01] ko ima ljubavi u sebi

505
00:17:07,339 --> 00:17:08,420
[SPEAKER_01] i više puta sam rekao,

506
00:17:08,420 --> 00:17:10,200
[SPEAKER_01] to ti je kompliment veliki,

507
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:12,099
[SPEAKER_01] želiko se teško ljuti,

508
00:17:12,099 --> 00:17:13,079
[SPEAKER_01] ali ako se naljuti,

509
00:17:13,079 --> 00:17:14,220
[SPEAKER_01] znači da si zaslužio.

510
00:17:14,220 --> 00:17:16,759
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to je moj dojam tebe,

511
00:17:16,759 --> 00:17:17,980
[SPEAKER_01] da imaš ljubav prema ljudima,

512
00:17:17,980 --> 00:17:18,500
[SPEAKER_01] da ti je Bog,

513
00:17:18,500 --> 00:17:20,019
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, evo,

514
00:17:20,019 --> 00:17:22,039
[SPEAKER_00] ne, da te puno ne hvalim,

515
00:17:22,119 --> 00:17:23,140
[SPEAKER_00] dobro, jako sigurno.

516
00:17:23,140 --> 00:17:24,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ima, bar se sad mogu

517
00:17:24,779 --> 00:17:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] sjetiti četvora ljude

518
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:26,980
[SPEAKER_00] na koje sam vikao.

519
00:17:26,980 --> 00:17:28,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ti su zaslužili,

520
00:17:28,559 --> 00:17:29,160
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam siguran.

521
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:37,880
[SPEAKER_00] Znak da sam uprostio Bogu

522
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:39,339
[SPEAKER_00] je da sad ne mogu

523
00:17:39,339 --> 00:17:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] više prestati pričati

524
00:17:40,539 --> 00:17:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] o njegove ljubavi.

525
00:17:41,519 --> 00:17:43,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ima dana kad mi se ne sviđa

526
00:17:43,940 --> 00:17:44,779
[SPEAKER_00] kako me voli,

527
00:17:44,779 --> 00:17:46,500
[SPEAKER_00] kad kažem da me voli

528
00:17:46,500 --> 00:17:47,240
[SPEAKER_00] kao zubar,

529
00:17:47,240 --> 00:17:49,200
[SPEAKER_00] da čini ono što je,

530
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:50,920
[SPEAKER_00] da mi buši,

531
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:52,200
[SPEAKER_00] stani mirno, stani mirno,

532
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:53,299
[SPEAKER_00] opusti se, opusti se.

533
00:17:53,299 --> 00:17:56,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ali uvijek sam uvjera

534
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:58,200
[SPEAKER_00] da je to sve što Bog radi

535
00:17:58,200 --> 00:17:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] je iz ljubavi,

536
00:17:59,019 --> 00:18:03,180
[SPEAKER_00] čak i kad su situacije bolne,

537
00:18:03,180 --> 00:18:04,640
[SPEAKER_00] kad me plaši,

538
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:07,859
[SPEAKER_00] kad je crnilo predavnom,

539
00:18:07,859 --> 00:18:09,160
[SPEAKER_00] ali znam,

540
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:12,140
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu sumnjati

541
00:18:12,140 --> 00:18:13,160
[SPEAKER_00] u Božju ljubav,

542
00:18:13,160 --> 00:18:16,259
[SPEAKER_00] jer je to tako iskustvo,

543
00:18:16,259 --> 00:18:17,160
[SPEAKER_00] toliko konkretno,

544
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] koje sam imao,

545
00:18:20,660 --> 00:18:25,940
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu sumnjati u tu ljubav.

546
00:18:25,940 --> 00:18:27,660
[SPEAKER_00] može se dogoditi

547
00:18:27,660 --> 00:18:28,900
[SPEAKER_00] da pobjegnem od nje

548
00:18:28,900 --> 00:18:29,920
[SPEAKER_00] ili nešto,

549
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:30,660
[SPEAKER_01] ali...

550
00:18:30,660 --> 00:18:31,220
[SPEAKER_01] Divno, divno.

551
00:18:31,220 --> 00:18:31,940
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala ti, brate.

552
00:18:31,940 --> 00:18:36,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ti možeš dodati još nešto slobodno.

553
00:18:36,039 --> 00:18:38,680
[SPEAKER_01] U medijima je Željko postao poznat

554
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:39,579
[SPEAKER_01] prije par godina,

555
00:18:39,579 --> 00:18:41,480
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam čitao večernjem listu,

556
00:18:41,480 --> 00:18:43,339
[SPEAKER_01] jer bi imao jedan slučaj u Americi,

557
00:18:43,339 --> 00:18:45,099
[SPEAKER_01] jedna žena došla se,

558
00:18:45,099 --> 00:18:46,859
[SPEAKER_01] on nikad nije rekao to iz ispovedi,

559
00:18:46,859 --> 00:18:47,460
[SPEAKER_01] to je ona rekla,

560
00:18:47,460 --> 00:18:47,880
[SPEAKER_01] naravno,

561
00:18:48,220 --> 00:18:49,599
[SPEAKER_01] najveća kazna za svećernika.

562
00:18:49,599 --> 00:18:50,859
[SPEAKER_01] Ako kaže nešto iz ispovedi,

563
00:18:50,859 --> 00:18:52,440
[SPEAKER_01] onda je eskomunicirana,

564
00:18:52,440 --> 00:18:53,240
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, svećernik je.

565
00:18:54,500 --> 00:18:56,240
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da nije on o tome govorio,

566
00:18:56,240 --> 00:18:57,859
[SPEAKER_01] nego ta žena je došla na ispovedi

567
00:18:57,859 --> 00:18:59,180
[SPEAKER_01] i priznala je,

568
00:18:59,180 --> 00:19:01,940
[SPEAKER_01] ispovedila da je lažno optušila čovjeka

569
00:19:01,940 --> 00:19:02,700
[SPEAKER_01] za silovanje,

570
00:19:02,700 --> 00:19:04,500
[SPEAKER_01] koji je završio u zatvoru zbog toga.

571
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:05,619
[SPEAKER_01] I onda Željko, normalno,

572
00:19:05,619 --> 00:19:06,640
[SPEAKER_01] šta će drugo reći,

573
00:19:06,640 --> 00:19:08,680
[SPEAKER_01] nego ne mogu vam dati odrešenje,

574
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:11,480
[SPEAKER_01] dok, ako ste ga javno oklevetali,

575
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,180
[SPEAKER_01] on ispašta,

576
00:19:12,180 --> 00:19:14,380
[SPEAKER_01] morate javno svjedočiti

577
00:19:14,380 --> 00:19:17,380
[SPEAKER_01] da je prouzet odgovornost

578
00:19:17,380 --> 00:19:18,299
[SPEAKER_01] i reći da ste lagali.

579
00:19:18,299 --> 00:19:19,660
[SPEAKER_01] I žena je to napravila.

580
00:19:19,660 --> 00:19:22,119
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je to bilo u medijima

581
00:19:22,119 --> 00:19:23,180
[SPEAKER_01] u Hrvatskoj je bilo medijima,

582
00:19:23,180 --> 00:19:24,299
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam čitao večernjaku,

583
00:19:24,299 --> 00:19:26,079
[SPEAKER_01] zaključak večernjaka je bio

584
00:19:26,079 --> 00:19:28,220
[SPEAKER_01] zašto najbolje svećernike izvozimo

585
00:19:28,220 --> 00:19:29,539
[SPEAKER_01] u inozemstvo?

586
00:19:29,539 --> 00:19:33,539
[SPEAKER_01] I sad si bio obrosi,

587
00:19:33,539 --> 00:19:35,579
[SPEAKER_01] i sada dobio je tri godine

588
00:19:35,579 --> 00:19:36,759
[SPEAKER_01] od svog biskupa da ide malo

589
00:19:36,759 --> 00:19:37,779
[SPEAKER_01] u misije,

590
00:19:37,779 --> 00:19:39,740
[SPEAKER_01] bio je dugo župnik tamo u župa,

591
00:19:39,740 --> 00:19:40,779
[SPEAKER_01] mu se zvala Empire,

592
00:19:40,779 --> 00:19:41,660
[SPEAKER_01] carstvo,

593
00:19:41,660 --> 00:19:43,099
[SPEAKER_01] na jednom prekrasnom jezeru,

594
00:19:43,099 --> 00:19:44,339
[SPEAKER_01] slavo mi je slike.

595
00:19:44,339 --> 00:19:45,099
[SPEAKER_01] I sad je dobio tri,

596
00:19:45,099 --> 00:19:47,640
[SPEAKER_01] pošto je Željko ušao na neukatekumenski put,

597
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:48,599
[SPEAKER_01] tražio je,

598
00:19:48,599 --> 00:19:49,619
[SPEAKER_01] mogu ja to skratiti,

599
00:19:50,140 --> 00:19:51,460
[SPEAKER_01] tražio je od svog župnika,

600
00:19:51,460 --> 00:19:51,880
[SPEAKER_01] dajete mi,

601
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:52,660
[SPEAKER_01] imao sam to iskuslo,

602
00:19:52,660 --> 00:19:53,960
[SPEAKER_01] dajete mi da malo upoznam Boga,

603
00:19:53,960 --> 00:19:54,960
[SPEAKER_01] što znači biti kršćanim,

604
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:56,720
[SPEAKER_01] župnik nije znao što će s njima,

605
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:57,640
[SPEAKER_01] da je rekao,

606
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:58,059
[SPEAKER_01] pa slušaj,

607
00:19:58,059 --> 00:20:00,519
[SPEAKER_01] sad dolaze dva para zaručnika

608
00:20:00,519 --> 00:20:01,819
[SPEAKER_01] na pripreme za brak,

609
00:20:01,819 --> 00:20:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] pa dođi s njima,

610
00:20:02,380 --> 00:20:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] tako da je Željko slušao župnika

611
00:20:04,960 --> 00:20:06,240
[SPEAKER_01] sa zaručnicima,

612
00:20:06,240 --> 00:20:09,099
[SPEAKER_01] pripremajući se s njima za brak,

613
00:20:09,099 --> 00:20:10,079
[SPEAKER_01] ali poslije otkriju,

614
00:20:10,079 --> 00:20:12,539
[SPEAKER_01] neukatekumenski put upravo zato služi,

615
00:20:12,700 --> 00:20:13,980
[SPEAKER_01] to je katekumenat,

616
00:20:13,980 --> 00:20:15,700
[SPEAKER_01] koji danas je izgubio,

617
00:20:15,700 --> 00:20:17,640
[SPEAKER_01] da nas neko uvodi,

618
00:20:17,640 --> 00:20:18,799
[SPEAKER_01] ne samo informativno,

619
00:20:18,799 --> 00:20:19,880
[SPEAKER_01] nego formativno,

620
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:21,119
[SPEAKER_01] da nas formira,

621
00:20:21,119 --> 00:20:22,339
[SPEAKER_01] da nas uči molit,

622
00:20:22,339 --> 00:20:23,440
[SPEAKER_01] da nas uči što je križ,

623
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:25,819
[SPEAKER_01] da nas uči slušat riječ Božju.

624
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:27,900
[SPEAKER_00] Da, to je možda dobra stvar

625
00:20:27,900 --> 00:20:30,019
[SPEAKER_00] da se kaže onak katekumenskom putu.

626
00:20:30,019 --> 00:20:33,220
[SPEAKER_00] Često puta pripremamo ljude za sakramente

627
00:20:33,220 --> 00:20:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] u nastavi, kao u razredu.

628
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:37,339
[SPEAKER_00] Informativno.

629
00:20:37,339 --> 00:20:37,900
[SPEAKER_00] Informativno.

630
00:20:37,900 --> 00:20:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] I djecu na krizni.

631
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:39,400
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

632
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:40,740
[SPEAKER_00] Neka pitanja.

633
00:20:40,740 --> 00:20:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] A to ti je kao da učiš plivanje

634
00:20:43,920 --> 00:20:45,200
[SPEAKER_00] gledajući YouTube,

635
00:20:45,200 --> 00:20:52,099
[SPEAKER_00] ili da učiš borilačke vištine

636
00:20:52,099 --> 00:20:54,759
[SPEAKER_00] gledajući filmove Bruce Lee.

637
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] ali dok ne živiš u jednoj zajednici,

638
00:20:58,039 --> 00:21:00,460
[SPEAKER_00] jer na kraju krajeva Bog je zajedništvo

639
00:21:00,460 --> 00:21:01,740
[SPEAKER_00] tri osobe.

640
00:21:01,740 --> 00:21:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] Zato nas uči kako živiti u vjeri,

641
00:21:04,579 --> 00:21:06,319
[SPEAKER_00] u zajedništvu sa drugima.

642
00:21:06,319 --> 00:21:09,099
[SPEAKER_01] Nekad je bilo evanđelje o mladiću,

643
00:21:09,099 --> 00:21:09,920
[SPEAKER_01] još samo ovo ću reći,

644
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:10,420
[SPEAKER_01] ako smijem,

645
00:21:10,420 --> 00:21:11,779
[SPEAKER_01] a ti ako nećeš prihvatiti,

646
00:21:11,779 --> 00:21:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću to u montaju.

647
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:15,680
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je evanđelje o bogatom mladiću

648
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:17,819
[SPEAKER_01] kojim je Krist rekao da prodav sve ide za njim

649
00:21:17,819 --> 00:21:18,819
[SPEAKER_01] i onda je otišao tužan.

650
00:21:18,819 --> 00:21:20,799
[SPEAKER_01] A bio je na misli samo Željko.

651
00:21:20,799 --> 00:21:21,559
[SPEAKER_01] Imam je paro napamet,

652
00:21:21,559 --> 00:21:22,279
[SPEAKER_01] cijetlio sam se,

653
00:21:22,279 --> 00:21:24,380
[SPEAKER_01] jer kad je Željko doživio obraćenje,

654
00:21:24,380 --> 00:21:25,779
[SPEAKER_01] došao na neukategonomijski put,

655
00:21:25,779 --> 00:21:28,160
[SPEAKER_01] Bog mi je dao voziv za svećenika,

656
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:30,460
[SPEAKER_01] onda je trebao ić u sveć u sjemenište

657
00:21:30,460 --> 00:21:31,339
[SPEAKER_01] i prodao je sve,

658
00:21:31,339 --> 00:21:32,240
[SPEAKER_01] i kujuštu sam,

659
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:33,180
[SPEAKER_01] šta si moj kuću,

660
00:21:33,180 --> 00:21:34,200
[SPEAKER_01] prodao je sve,

661
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:34,839
[SPEAKER_01] dao ča,

662
00:21:34,839 --> 00:21:36,319
[SPEAKER_01] ostavio je samo biciklu.

663
00:21:36,319 --> 00:21:38,339
[SPEAKER_01] I šta se dogodilo s biciklom?

664
00:21:38,720 --> 00:21:40,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ukrali su mi biciklu.

665
00:21:40,019 --> 00:21:41,339
[SPEAKER_00] I onda si kupio drugu,

666
00:21:41,339 --> 00:21:42,180
[SPEAKER_00] ukrali su i tu.

667
00:21:42,180 --> 00:21:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer još sam imao dvije,

668
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:45,779
[SPEAKER_00] rekao imat ću još dvije plaće,

669
00:21:45,779 --> 00:21:46,920
[SPEAKER_00] šta će s tim novcima,

670
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:49,160
[SPEAKER_00] pa mogu si još opet kupit biciklu.

671
00:21:49,160 --> 00:21:49,920
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, eto.

672
00:21:49,920 --> 00:21:51,059
[SPEAKER_00] I eto, ukrali mi je.

673
00:21:51,059 --> 00:21:53,559
[SPEAKER_01] I onda sam zaključio propoved bio neki dan,

674
00:21:53,559 --> 00:21:55,240
[SPEAKER_01] jer taj mladić je otišao žalostan,

675
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:55,839
[SPEAKER_01] jer nije mogao,

676
00:21:55,839 --> 00:21:56,859
[SPEAKER_01] a ja Željka nalazim,

677
00:21:56,859 --> 00:21:58,559
[SPEAKER_01] sad ne znam koliko godina se nismo vidjeli,

678
00:21:58,559 --> 00:21:59,960
[SPEAKER_01] nalazim ga još uvijek,

679
00:21:59,960 --> 00:22:00,819
[SPEAKER_01] nakon svih tih godina,

680
00:22:00,940 --> 00:22:02,140
[SPEAKER_01] veselog i vedrog.

681
00:22:02,140 --> 00:22:06,200
[SPEAKER_01] Eto, tako ostani Željko do kraja.

682
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:08,440
[SPEAKER_01] Pozdrav svima.

683
00:22:08,440 --> 00:22:09,160
[SPEAKER_01] Pozdrav.

